    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Periclimenes manihine sp. nov., holotype. Scale bar in millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173832>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Periclimenes manihine sp. nov. A, carapace and antennal peduncles. B, anterior carapace and rostrum. C, antennule. D, antenna. E, eye. F, third pereiopod distal propod and dactyl. G, telson. H, same, posterior spines. I, uropod. J, same, exopod, posterolateral angle. A, holotype, B – J, paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173832/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173833>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Periclimenes manihine sp. nov., paratype.. A, first pereiopod. B, same, chela. C, major second pereiopod. D, same, chela. E, same. F, same, merus. G, minor second pereiopod, chela." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173834>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Periclimenes manihine sp. nov., paratype.. A, major second pereiopod, fingers, dorsal. B, same, tips of fingers, medial aspect. C, minor second pereiopod, tips of fingers, ventral view D, third pereiopod, propod and dactyl. E, same, propod, ventral spine. F, first pleopod. G, same, endopod. H, second pleopod. I, same, endopod. J, same appendix masculina and appendix interna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173834/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

